# Admin Panel

The application uses Filament for its admin interface, providing a powerful dashboard for managing RSVPs and parties.

## Resources
- [app/Filament/Resources/RsvpResource.php](mdc:app/Filament/Resources/RsvpResource.php) - Manages RSVP entries
- [app/Filament/Resources/PartyResource.php](mdc:app/Filament/Resources/PartyResource.php) - Manages party configurations
- [app/Filament/Resources/UserResource.php](mdc:app/Filament/Resources/UserResource.php) - Manages user records

## Widgets
- [app/Filament/Widgets/RsvpCount.php](mdc:app/Filament/Widgets/RsvpCount.php) - Displays RSVP statistics

## Key Features
- Full CRUD operations for RSVPs, Parties, and Users
- Stats overview widget for RSVP tracking
- Resource relationships management
- Form-based data entry and validation
- Table-based data display with sorting and filtering

## Access Control
- Admin interface is protected by authentication
- Users must implement the FilamentUser interface
- Custom middleware stack for security
- Configurable through [config/filament.php](mdc:config/filament.php)
